<paragraph blockId="17.[132,777,702,806]" pageId="17" pageNumber="66">
NOTES. — It seems very likely that the record by 
<bibRefCitation author="DI CAPORIACCO L." pageId="17" pageNumber="66" pagination="1 - 4" refId="ref60111" refString="DI CAPORIACCO L. 1928. - Aracnidi. Il Parco Nazionale del Gran Paradiso, Torino 2: 1 - 4." type="journal article" year="1928">di Caporiacco (1928)</bibRefCitation>
refers to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Herve, Roberts &amp; Murphy" authorityYear="2009" box="[303,402,729,753]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Drassodex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="17" pageNumber="66" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="drescoi">
<emphasis box="[303,402,729,753]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="66">D. drescoi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, distributed in North-Western Alps. Unlikely, 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Pavesi" baseAuthorityYear="1873" box="[229,307,755,779]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Drassodex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="17" pageNumber="66" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="heeri">
<emphasis box="[229,307,755,779]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="66">D. heeri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is a Central Alpine species (Hervé 
<emphasis box="[662,711,755,779]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="66">et al.</emphasis>
2009; 
<bibRefCitation author="HANGGI A. &amp; STAUBLI A." box="[134,370,782,806]" pageId="17" pageNumber="66" pagination="59 - 76" refId="ref60241" refString="HANGGI A. &amp; STAUBLI A. 2012. - Nachtrage zum &quot; Katalog der schweizerischen Spinnen &quot; 4. Neunachweise von 2002 bis 2011. Arachnologische Mitteilungen 44: 59 - 76." type="journal article" year="2012">Hänggi &amp; Stäubli 2012</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
